  <brief_title>Compare the Efficacy of Acupuncture Therapy and Carbamazepine Oral Dosage in Patients With Carpal Tunnel Syndrome by Multiple Excitability Test</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-center, Prospective, Randomized, Positive Controlled, Parallel Design Trial to Compare the Efficacy of Acupuncture Therapy and Carbamazepine Oral Dosage in Patients With Carpal Tunnel Syndrome by Multiple Excitability Test</official_title>
